(172, '_transient_0e09669bc4eb6aa3ee6183997a4a0d96', 'O:8:\"stdClass\":27:{s:4:\"name\";s:23:\"Rewrite Rules Inspector\";s:4:\"slug\";s:23:\"rewrite-rules-inspector\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.2.1\";s:6:\"author\";s:65:\"<a href=\"http://automattic.com/\">Daniel Bachhuber, Automattic</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:41:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/automattic\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"3.1\";s:6:\"tested\";s:6:\"4.8.11\";s:12:\"requires_php\";b:0;s:13:\"compatibility\";a:0:{}s:6:\"rating\";d:100;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:22;i:4;i:1;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:0;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:23;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:1;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:160844;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2017-06-08 2:35pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2012-05-09\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:60:\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/rewrite-rules-inspector/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:3:{s:11:\"description\";s:746:\"<p>A straightforward WordPress admin tool for inspecting your rewrite rules. View a listing of all your rewrite rules, see which rewrite rules match a given URL (and the priorites they match in), or filter by different sources of rewrite rules. Perform a soft flush of your rewrite rules to regenerate them.</p>\n<p>Originally developed for <a href=\"http://vip.wordpress.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress.com VIP</a>-hosted clients, we thought it would be useful for development environments, etc. too. Feel free to <a href=\"https://github.com/Automattic/Rewrite-Rules-Inspector/\" rel=\"nofollow\">fork the plugin in Github</a> — pull requests are always welcome. Hit us with feedback, questions, bug reports, and feature requests in the forums.</p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:947:\"<h4>1.2.1 (Sept. 19, 2013)</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix for strict standards error in declaration of Rewrite_Rules_Inspector_List_Table::single_row(). props @simonhampel</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2 (Jan. 16, 2013)</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Modify the rewrite rule source with a filter. Props <a href=\"https://github.com/jeremyfelt\" rel=\"nofollow\">jeremyfelt</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1 (Sept. 25, 2012)</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Support for route matching when WordPress lives in a subdirectory. Props <a href=\"https://github.com/dbernar1\" rel=\"nofollow\">dbernar1</a></li>\n<li>Display a success message after you&#8217;ve flushed your rewrite rules</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0 (May 9, 2012)</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial public release!</li>\n<li>View a listing of all your rewrite rules</li>\n<li>See which rewrite rules match a given URL (and the priorites they match in)</li>\n<li>Filter by different sources of rewrite rules</li>\n<li>Error message appears if rewrite rules are missing in the database</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:691:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/rewrite-rules-inspector/trunk/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1776987\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/rewrite-rules-inspector/trunk/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1776987\" alt=\"See which rewrite rules match a given URL (and the priorites they match in)\"></a><p>See which rewrite rules match a given URL (and the priorites they match in)</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/rewrite-rules-inspector/trunk/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1776987\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/rewrite-rules-inspector/trunk/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1776987\" alt=\"Error message appears if rewrite rules are missing in the database\"></a><p>Error message appears if rewrite rules are missing in the database</p></li></ol>\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/rewrite-rules-inspector.1.2.1.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:2:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:75:\"https://ps.w.org/rewrite-rules-inspector/trunk/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1776987\";s:7:\"caption\";s:75:\"See which rewrite rules match a given URL (and the priorites they match in)\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:75:\"https://ps.w.org/rewrite-rules-inspector/trunk/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1776987\";s:7:\"caption\";s:66:\"Error message appears if rewrite rules are missing in the database\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:2:{s:13:\"rewrite-rules\";s:13:\"rewrite rules\";s:5:\"tools\";s:5:\"tools\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:5:{s:3:\"1.0\";s:70:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/rewrite-rules-inspector.1.0.zip\";s:3:\"1.1\";s:70:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/rewrite-rules-inspector.1.1.zip\";s:3:\"1.2\";s:70:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/rewrite-rules-inspector.1.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.1\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/rewrite-rules-inspector.1.2.1.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/rewrite-rules-inspector.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"author_block_count\";i:0;s:19:\"author_block_rating\";d:100;s:12:\"contributors\";a:0:{}}', 'no'),
